window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Bianca's prison has a way out, but the price of freedom is high.</b></p> <p>There is more to Bianca's struggles than meets the eye, and even she ignores the depth of the trail she must follow to get her revenge against the Black King.</p> <p>Through the machinations of fate, she discovers her life is more intertwined to Nyro's than she ever imagined. They share a purpose, but is she willing to accept the consequences to attain what she set out to do when she joined the White Court?</p> <p><b>Immerse yourself in Vampire Court, an addicting fantasy series by </b><b><i>USA Today </i></b><b>best-selling author Ingrid Seymour.</b></p>"; 
